{
  "stem": "10644.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I revolted, and I said I'm not going to cheder.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wanted to go, you know, to-- to go-- start to go-- thinking about going to a gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eight-- eight and a half years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I revolted.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is the only time that my father came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gave me a spanking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went for one day to the cheder.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I came back, and I say, I'm not going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Year my grandfather came-- probably some-- somehow my father informed-- my grandmother came and took me away to Vyazma.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just to go away from Barisaw, from this-- from this, oh, you know, form of life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, he took to me to-- to Vyazma.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my-- my mother was in Vyazma.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed for eight, nine months in Vyazma-- almost-- and I was making preparations to enter a Russian-- it is called gymnasia-- eight year, from 10 years admitted, to approximately to [? 80 ?] years, you know, age.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a government-- government school, government school, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were very-- in this-- in this [INAUDIBLE]-- maybe in the-- in Vyazma, maybe three or four Jews were in a whole-- the school.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I came back to Barisaw, Barisaw had a very large such gymnasia, you know, which, in each class, three-- three-- three equal-- equal classes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there, I took my test, and I was admitted to the gymnasium-- gymnasia in Barisaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was there only for one year.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Here, it was the time-- it was already a revolution, or already time, [INAUDIBLE] beginning the German occupation but--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1918.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1918, in-- in-- the Germans had to-- went-- or went already back to Germany, it was already after the war, and approximately the time of-- of the war.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
